description: Named after a warm Mediterranean wind, the 2017 Maserati Levante is engineered to master any situation effortlessly. The Levante provides the highest levels of comfort all while delivering outstanding performance in the most extreme conditions. Masteratis first-ever SUV comes standard with an eight-speed gearbox as well as Q4 AWD and torque vectoring system. Its interior comes highly customizable with up to 28 different color combinations from premium leather and fine woods to Ermenegildo Zegna silk  Levantes interiors are a feast of excellence. An eight-speaker audio system comes standard with the option to upgrade to a 14-speaker, 900-watt or 17-speaker, 1280-watt system. Sporting a 3.0 Twin Turbo V6 petrol engine and offering no fewer than three types of engines to choose from, including two direct-injected gasoline versions in 345 and 424 horsepower states of tune along with one diesel six that comes in at 271 horsepower, Maserati continues to deliver incredible levels of performance. Always keeping safety in mind, the Levante comes equipped with six dual-stage airbags, active headrests, and a tire pressure monitoring system. The Rear Cross Path, which emits sound when an unseen vehicle is detected from the sides, aids the driver in backing out of a parking space. It also has built in Hill Descent Control to ensure a smooth downhill ride without the driver needing to touch the brake pedal. Thanks to both the blind spot alert and Lane Departure Warning System, the driver can rest assured of their surroundings and focus on the road ahead of them. 100% sports utility vehicle, 100% Maserati.***ONLINE PRICE IS FOR CASH PURCHASES. COMPETITIVE FINANCING AND LEASE OPTIONS ARE AVAILABLE. ALL PRICES DO NOT REFLECT A DESTINATION SURCHARGE OF $995. PRICES INCLUDE ALL MANUFACTURER REBATES AND DEALER INCENTIVES. MUST TAKE DELIVERY FROM DEALER STOCK BY 7/31/2017.***.

description: Ford F-150 capability is legendary in the world of hardworking pickups. But think F-150 capability has been outstanding in the past? The 2016 F-150 is remarkably stronger, yet lighter by 700lbs. The body of the new F-150 is high-strength, military grade, aluminum alloy - delivering best-in-class maximum towing and payload. Greater strength with less weight achieves a 3,300-lb. maximum payload rating that is best-in-class. Even the F-150 powered by the new 2.7L EcoBoost V6 can haul up to 2,250 lbs. when properly equipped. The 3.5L Ti-VCT FFV V6 is engineered to handle demanding everyday jobs and has a 5 percent better power-to-weight ratio than the previous 3.7L V6, towing up to 7,600 lbs. The 3.5L V6 puts out 283 horsepower and 255 lb. ft. of torque. The available 3.5L EcoBoost V6 power ratings are quite impressive at 365hp and 420 lb. ft. of torque. The durable 5.0L V8 has a better power-to-weight ratio with 385hp and 387 lb. ft. torque. The 3.5L EcoBoost V6, in fact, delivers a best-in-class 12,200-lb. maximum tow rating. New Ford innovations will keep you working through all conditions; the BoxLink all-new configurable universal pickup box interface system secures a wide variety of available Ford and aftermarket accessories such as ramps, storage bins, dividers and many others including E-Track. LED Box Lights, stowable loading ramps, 110 volt AC plug-in-outlet and remote tailgate release systems are all available options and ways that the F-150 will make your life a little easier. Get comfortable after a hard day in the comfort of your cab, with the available new 8-inch LCD Productivity Screen provides useful information from fuel economy to towing data right in front of you.UP TO $16 000 OFF MSRP ONLY AT LORENZO FORD!Turbocharged.
title: 2016 Ford F-150
